Abominus pulled himself to his feet, and tried to shield his face with 
his massive arms, the blasts from Galaxor's firepower blowing up all 
over his frame, leaving gashes and blackened spots of armor. "Hrrrr, 
gruan grrrrrrraaaaaaaaa" he shrieked, as he leapt forward, to try to 
grab Galaxor.
